&quot;The Seed-become-Harvester must swear upon their own blood, that they will abide by the Code of Conduct of the Violent Harvest, that they will remain true to the vision of the Violent Harvest, and that they will do all that they can to aid others so bound to the vision. The oath must be concluded with this, &quot;Let Innoruuk bind my blood in stone if I fail&quot;. This is the Oath of Binding.&quot;<br>
Violent Harvest Charter pg. whatever paragraph whatever <br>
